snippet.title: Chess Ultimate Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2580000/Chess_Ultimate/

Online turn based strategy game based on chess.
Make a team to battle against other players.  
Each character has a unique trait and are balanced by a point system.  
Knock out the enemy's King to win a match.
